title: Watch This Space
description: A quick breakdown on what the Court did and didn’t do today (Friday, October 22) in the cases against Texas's S.B. 8, which prohibits abortion 6 week's after the pregnant person's last period.
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
